name: JI Shogi-Themed Lichess (2-Kanji)
description: Shogi-Themed Chess on Lichess. Play chess in shogi (Japanese Chess) design on Lichess. Shogi is the Japanese cousin of western chess and you can now play using its 2-kanji design on Lichess. You can read more about JI Shogi-Themed Chess here.
additional_info:
-Pieces and Board included.
-Make sure to select any of the first 25 board theme to get the Shogi board design.
-Works with puzzles and analysis.
